          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. In this experiment, the difficulty is to",
                "determine the number of target deuterons in the D+D",
                "reaction. Since, the deuterons are accumulated in metal",
                "plate during the deuteron bombardment, the number of",
                "target deuterons changes."
              ]
            }
          ],
